        <Meaning id="8a029080-8445-4098-a226-1fb8605cd7a9" type="Noun">
          <Vi>điều tra viên; nhà điều tra</Vi>
          <En>a person whose job is to investigate crimes or other problems, especially by collecting and examining evidence</En>
          <Example>The investigator reviewed surveillance footage to identify the suspect.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
